# ============================================================
# TCSS DASHBOARD - PRODUCTION PREMIUM V14
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Single-file Streamlit dashboard for THAI Customer Satisfaction Survey.
# Production notes:
# - Automatic desktop / smartphone rendering by user-agent + query override.
# - No landing-page blocker; dashboard opens directly.
# - Plotly charts use a single executive board-deck theme.
# - KPI cards, tables, legends, and chart spacing are optimized for readability.
# - V4 reduces header clutter, uses full-width chart rows for dense views,
#   and renders heat maps as country choropleths instead of circle markers.
# - V5 keeps Plotly toolbar / PNG export / fullscreen-ready chart elements.
# - V6 compresses chart heights to reduce vertical scrolling.
# - V10 compacts the sidebar, removes Executive metric copy, and fixes Station Summary numeric sorting.
# - V11 adds period-aware Station Summary cards and rule-based Top Commendation by Topic.
# - V12 adds touchpoint-change auto scroll-to-top, cleans Total Responses card wording,
#   and upgrades the premium THAI tri-color page background system.
# - V13 enforces top-scroll on every touchpoint change and moves Commendation Topic / Topic Count
#   to the final columns in the Top Commendation table.
# - V9 strengthens the THAI 66th anniversary sidebar identity, compacts legends,
#   and places Gender / Age / Purpose profile donuts in one executive row.
# - V15 keeps V14 fixes and adds automatic Complaint_Raw consolidation into Summary Complaint Detail.xlsx.
# - HTML/CSS is placeholder-safe; no CSS f-string interpolation is used.
# ============================================================


